DE_DELTAMILL

Created by: Wheel-Knee
Contact: johnlawrance@gmail.com
Release Date: March 07/2005
Capacity: 32 vs. 32 (64)
Works with Bots: Yes (watch for updated NAV on www.punkassfraggers.com)

OBJECTIVE

Terrorists must bomb the mill stockpiles, or the dam to disable food production. CTs must protect their mill, and foodstocks for Delta.

This map is based on an Old Stone Mill built in 1810 in Delta Ontario. It was build by a loyalist and industrialist from Vermont. This mill is one of the oldest surviving mills in Ontario and is a example of early Canadian Architecture, and pioneer industrial development.

Enjoy
